<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{subject}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2196F3;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-left: 4px solid #f39c12;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .transaction-details {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .transaction-details h3 {
            color: #d32f2f;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .transaction-details ul {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #2196F3;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">AL Agent Platform</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2 style="color: #d32f2f;">ðŸš¨ Flagged Transaction Alert</h2>
        <p>Dear User,</p>
        <p>This is a notification for a flagged transaction that requires your attention.</p>
        
        <div class="transaction-details">
            <h3>Transaction Details:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Transaction ID:</strong> {{transactionId}}</li>
                <li><strong>Amount:</strong> {{amount}}</li>
                <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</li>
                <li><strong>Status:</strong> <span style="color: #d32f2f;">{{status}}</span></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="alert-box">
            <strong>Action Required:</strong> Please review this transaction and take appropriate action through your dashboard.
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        
        <p>
            Best regards,<br>
            <strong>AL Support Team</strong>
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} AL Agent Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
